original_title: Ayumi Hamasaki - M(A)DE IN JAPAN [LIMITED TA LIVE TOUR at Zepp Tokyo]
overview: Ayumi Hamasaki performing her album Made in Japan (stylized as M(A)DE IN JAPAN). Recorded on November 17, 2016, the final night of the TA LIMITED LIVE TOUR 2016, at the Zepp DiverCity music hall in Tokyo.
title: Ayumi Hamasaki - M(A)DE IN JAPAN [LIMITED TA LIVE TOUR at Zepp Tokyo]
